OL,3,CMinimum age for train drivers to be
OL,4,Clowered to 18 amid shortage
OL,6,FThe Government hopes cutting the age
OL,7,Fat which people can qualify as a train
OL,8,Fdriver will reduce this reliance on
OL,9,Frest day working.
OL,11,FIt said 87% of cancellations made the
OL,12,Fnight before a service is scheduled to
OL,13,Frun are caused by driver shortages.
OL,15,FThe average age of a UK train driver
OL,16,Fis 48, with 30% set to reach
OL,17,Fretirement age by 2029.
OL,19,FFewer than 9% of train drivers are
OL,20,Ffemale, while under 12% are from an
OL,21,Fethnic minority.
