OL,6,F"We're committed to getting the
OL,7,Feconomy moving and a big part of that
OL,8,Fis getting young people into the
OL,9,Fworkforce, putting them on track for a
OL,10,Fskilled and fulfilling career which
OL,11,Fwill boost growth across the country
OL,12,Fand help deliver our Plan for Change.
OL,14,F"We're future-proofing our railways
OL,15,Fagainst delays and cancellations
OL,16,Fcaused by a shortage of drivers,
OL,17,Fensuring that we can provide reliable,
OL,18,Fpassenger-focused train journeys under
OL,19,FGreat British Railways (GBR) for
OL,20,Fdecades to come."
