OL,3,CMinimum age for train drivers to be
OL,4,Clowered to 18 amid shortage
OL,6,FThe Government plans to establish GBR
OL,7,Fas a new public sector body which will
OL,8,Foversee rail infrastructure management
OL,9,Fand train operation.
OL,11,FMick Whelan, general secretary of
OL,12,Ftrain drivers' union Aslef, said: "At
OL,13,Fthe moment, young people who want to
OL,14,Fbecome train drivers leave school or
OL,15,Fcollege at 18, get other jobs, and we
OL,16,Fmiss out as an industry as they don't
OL,17,Fwait around until they turn 20 to find
OL,18,Fa career."
