OL,6,FHe added that the new policy will
OL,7,F"increase diversity in the driver's
OL,8,Fcab" as well as encouraging more young
OL,9,Fpeople to take on the role.
OL,11,FAmong other nations that have lowered
OL,12,Fthe age for train drivers are France,
OL,13,FGermany, the Netherlands and
OL,14,FSwitzerland, according to the DfT.
OL,16,FTransport for London opened up its
OL,17,Ftrain driver apprenticeships on the
OL,18,FUnderground to 18-year-olds in 2007.
