OL,11,Fbefore the minimum age can be lowered.
OL,13,FThis includes the industry developing
OL,14,Fplans to integrate younger employees,
OL,15,Fand amending existing laws.
OL,17,FAssessment and qualification standards
OL,18,Fwill be unchanged.
